msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/maskedarray.generic.rst:374
msgid ""
"As a :class:`MaskedArray` is a subclass of :class:`numpy.ndarray`, it "
"inherits its mechanisms for indexing and slicing."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/maskedarray.generic.rst:377
msgid ""
"When accessing a single entry of a masked array with no named fields, the "
"output is either a scalar (if the corresponding entry of the mask is "
"``False``) or the special value :attr:`masked` (if the corresponding entry "
"of the mask is ``True``):"
